  "description": "This dataset contains electroencephalography (EEG) recordings investigating the temporal dynamics of food representation in the human brain. The study employs BIDS-formatted raw EEG data to characterize how food-related information is processed and represented across different time windows during neural processing. Participants viewed images of food and non-food objects while EEG was recorded. This resource provides a foundation for understanding the neural mechanisms underlying food perception and cognition.",
